query: SELECT MIN(cn1.name) AS first_company, MIN(cn2.name) AS second_company, MIN(mi_idx1.info) AS first_rating, MIN(mi_idx2.info) AS second_rating, MIN(t1.title) AS first_movie, MIN(t2.title) AS second_movie FROM company_name AS cn1, company_name AS cn2, info_type AS it1, info_type AS it2, kind_type AS kt1, kind_type AS kt2, link_type AS lt, movie_companies AS mc1, movie_companies AS mc2, movie_info_idx AS mi_idx1, movie_info_idx AS mi_idx2, movie_link AS ml, title AS t1, title AS t2 WHERE lt.id = ml.link_type_id AND t1.id = ml.movie_id AND t2.id = ml.linked_movie_id AND it1.id = mi_idx1.info_type_id AND t1.id = mi_idx1.movie_id AND kt1.id = t1.kind_id AND cn1.id = mc1.company_id AND t1.id = mc1.movie_id AND ml.movie_id = mi_idx1.movie_id AND ml.movie_id = mc1.movie_id AND mi_idx1.movie_id = mc1.movie_id AND it2.id = mi_idx2.info_type_id AND t2.id = mi_idx2.movie_id AND kt2.id = t2.kind_id AND cn2.id = mc2.company_id AND t2.id = mc2.movie_id AND ml.linked_movie_id = mi_idx2.movie_id AND ml.linked_movie_id = mc2.movie_id AND mi_idx2.movie_id = mc2.movie_id AND cn1.country_code not in ('tl','gd','mv','la','gw') AND (mc1.note like '%International%' OR mc1.note like '%USA%' OR mc1.note like '%Sweden%' OR mc1.note like '%Brazil%') AND it2.info in ('novel','studios','votes','budget','gross','other literature','LD supplement','LD video quality','mpaa','opening weekend','LD contrast','trivia','agent address','sound mix','LD catalog number','admissions','LD analog left','LD dialogue intellegibility') AND kt1.kind not in ('tv movie','tv series','episode','tv mini series','video game','video movie') AND it1.info in ('adaption','crazy credits','rating','LD review') AND (mc2.note like '%UK%' OR mc2.note like '%Denmark%' OR mc2.note like '%Australia%') AND (t1.title like '%love%') AND (cn2.name like '%Pixar Animation Studios%' OR cn2.name like '%Walt Disney Studios%' OR cn2.name like '%A24%' OR cn2.name like '%Paramount Pictures%' OR cn2.name like '%Warner Bros. Pictures%') AND mi_idx2.info < '4.0' AND lt.link in ('featured in','spoofs','edited into','spin off from','referenced in','remake of','alternate language version of','followed by','edited from','unknown link') AND (t2.title like '%thriller%') AND mi_idx1.info > '8.0' AND kt2.kind in ('tv series','movie','video game')
